# Gradle
.gradle/
build/

## Kotlin Gradle Plugin (KGP 2.0+) project-level cache — klib metadata
## transformations of dependencies (`metadata/kotlinTransformedMetadataLibraries/`),
## error logs, and incremental-compile sessions. Regenerated on every
## clean build, never a source artifact.
.kotlin/

## Daemon JVM toolchain criteria auto-generated by Android Studio /
## `./gradlew updateDaemonJvm` from whatever JDK happens to be on the
## local machine (typically the IDE-bundled JBR / latest installed
## JDK). CI already pins Java 17 via `actions/setup-java@v5`, and
## committing the file would force the foojay-disco fallback to
## download a non-matching JDK every build. Each environment manages
## its own daemon JVM via JAVA_HOME / setup-java instead.
gradle/gradle-daemon-jvm.properties

